  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions - Execute approved mitigation actions]
  N5 --> N6[PB: UI Screens - Monitor and report launch performance]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS impact from launch delays and improved on-time delivery]
  N3 -->|High risk detected but no clear mitig...| B1[Escalate to war room for manual intervention]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual review and decision by war room team]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Low risk detected| B2[Automatically approve mitigation plan]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Immediate execution of mitigation actions without human review]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Mitigation plan rejected by CWB Lifec...| B3[Re-analyze risk factors and generate new mitigation plans]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Iterative refinement of mitigation strategies until approval]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]